{"tid":609499,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中國人怎麼可能幫台灣人」 劉樂妍慘遭報復","createTime":"2018-03-29T06:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T01:09:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a64633f54cc7928c7cd7af345043fa64b3599216","tid":609499,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:03:07.000Z","msg":"〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕前「女F4」團長劉樂妍昨晚怒氣沖天，在中國北京街上大罵「幹，刁民」，因為她想停車卻被中國鄉民擺地鎖，氣得向公安投訴，沒想到愛車竟被破壞。"},{"pid":"53b23f7d6847e12b6f6b20ef769d08d58dd8a4d1","tid":609499,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2380051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2380051&d=m0IYAp8BOsm1xMdwEBNi%2F5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=9944f1da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2380051&h=a9997b70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2380051</a>"},{"pid":"39394b2f9fcc6bef58de11dcddd8083e5e7170b0","tid":609499,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:07:52.000Z","msg":"稍早，剛起床的劉樂妍前去看她愛車，真的無緣無故被破壞，她無奈吐露：「員警先生，我的車子被人破壞放氣，先放了很多石頭，刮花我的車。」雖然愛車被破壞警告，劉樂妍還是天不怕地不怕說：「我現在要報警，就是這個流氓蜀源房屋。」然後po出疑似破壞她車子的店家。<br />\n有人提醒劉樂妍：「中國人還是偏向中國人。」因為她是「台灣人」啊。（翻攝自劉樂妍臉書）<br />\n雖然劉樂妍指控有可能都是真的，但她畢竟是「台灣人」，身在中國發展，怎麼還學不會凡事低調處理，有網友提醒她：「妳是境外人士，在中國要有謙卑心，這種事都是各說各有理。除了你的少數鐵粉外，從感情上，中國人還是偏向中國人。這種民事糾紛員警也不好管，你只能到法院交錢自訴。」狠狠打臉她。<br />\n稍早，劉樂妍怒火未消又再發文：「這人太可恨，他會拆鎖，我報警了。他居然把我行車記錄器都偷走！我的行車記錄器買2千多塊人民幣。」天啊！這東西被偷，劉樂妍當場又損失台幣逾1萬元。"},{"pid":"5f373bb2561f92b25fcc54f9ca06dcf46a64ebdf","tid":609499,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大陸人唔當台灣人係中國人"},{"pid":"293a3a5f45ea598b6865e7b47528b90e44ee25ad","tid":609499,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c0af424fc98de83af2761bbb670e264ffdd3d4","tid":609499,"uid":50663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"班蝗搞台獨"},{"pid":"0386c8648afb3fb0e5dffda75794e585d1d67b80","tid":609499,"uid":168171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:33:33.000Z","msg":"中國公安唔做嘢情願被台獨分子唱？"},{"pid":"948b947d26dc7eda77984e852cc1926b92fe777f","tid":609499,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T01:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php1E7d9L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php1E7d9L.jpg&h=2eec72f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/09/04/99/6773785.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F09%2F04%2F99%2F6773785.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&d=m0IYAp8BOsm1xMdwEBNi%2F5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=349b0a98\" target=\"_blank\">https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/09/04/99/6773785.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1539660942-59b2900aa03cb2182a51cdb520b535b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F1539660942-59b2900aa03cb2182a51cdb520b535b6.png&h=36c067d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p1-news.yamedia.tw/MjY2MDIyMzBuZXdz/8b755fc0353e8151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h